<section id="products" class="py-20 bg-dark-charcoal">
	<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="text-center mb-16">
			<h2 class="font-poppins font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl mb-6 text-gold">
				A Complete Digital Payment Ecosystem
			</h2>
			<p class="font-inter text-xl text-light-gray max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				Everything your business needs to accept payments, manage finances, and build customer loyalty.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
			<!-- Product 1: Branded Visa Cards -->
			<div class="bg-dark-blue rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl group">
				<div class="relative w-full h-[400px] flex items-center justify-center">
					<img 
						src="https://img.webniaga.my/firstclassbiz/kadvisa.png" 
						alt="Branded Visa Prepaid Cards"
						class="w-full h-full object-contain max-w-[400px]"
					/>
				</div>
				<div class="p-8">
				<h3 class="font-poppins font-semibold text-2xl text-gold mb-4 group-hover:text-yellow-400 transition-colors">
					Branded Visa Prepaid Cards
				</h3>
				<p class="font-inter text-light-gray leading-relaxed">
					Elevate your business with a Premium Edition Visa Prepaid Card, fully customized with your company's own branding. This solution is designed to build consumer confidence in local brands by providing a product with international Visa recognition, which enhances your professional image. The card seamlessly integrates with customer loyalty programs, providing tangible benefits that help attract and retain a larger customer base. It is a versatile tool that can be used for memberships, agent incentives, staff cards, and overall brand building.
				</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Product 2: Kash E-Wallet -->
			<div class="bg-dark-blue rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl group">
				<div class="relative w-full h-[400px] flex items-center justify-center">
					<img 
						src="https://img.webniaga.my/firstclassbiz/apps.png" 
						alt="Kash E-Wallet mobile app"
						class="w-full h-full object-contain max-w-[400px]"
					/>
				</div>
				<div class="p-8">
				<h3 class="font-poppins font-semibold text-2xl text-gold mb-4 group-hover:text-yellow-400 transition-colors">
					Kash POS App
				</h3>
				<p class="font-inter text-light-gray leading-relaxed">
					Allowed businesses to accept direct payments from customers using ATM or debit cards.
				</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Product 3: QR Payments -->
			<div class="bg-dark-blue rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl group">
				<div class="relative w-full h-[400px] flex items-center justify-center">
					<img 
						src="https://img.webniaga.my/firstclassbiz/qr.png" 
						alt="QR code payment system"
						class="w-full h-full object-contain max-w-[400px]"
					/>
				</div>
				<div class="p-8">
				<h3 class="font-poppins font-semibold text-2xl text-gold mb-4 group-hover:text-yellow-400 transition-colors">
					Merchant QR Payments
				</h3>
				<p class="font-inter text-light-gray leading-relaxed">
					Accept seamless payments via Malaysia National QR, with all funds deposited directly into your company's bank account. As a core component of the First Class Merchant payment application , this system offers a modern and flexible solution designed to support local entrepreneurs and SMEs.
				</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Product 4: POS Apps -->
			<div class="bg-dark-blue rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl group">
				<div class="relative w-full h-[400px] flex items-center justify-center">
					<img 
						src="https://img.webniaga.my/firstclassbiz/ewallet.png" 
						alt="Point of sale terminal"
						class="w-full h-full object-contain max-w-[400px]"
					/>
				</div>
				<div class="p-8">
				<h3 class="font-poppins font-semibold text-2xl text-gold mb-4 group-hover:text-yellow-400 transition-colors">
					Kash E-Wallet Apps
				</h3>
				<p class="font-inter text-light-gray leading-relaxed">
					Flexible and modern solutions for businesses to accept both QR and card payments effortlessly. A mobile application that gives customers access to a secure digital e-wallet. A key feature of this wallet is KA$H Rebates, allowing users to earn automatic cash back from participating retailers, which can then be spent in-app or withdrawn to their bank.
				</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>